<h2 id="getting-started">Getting Started</h2>
<p>To get a local copy up and running follow these simple steps.</p>

<h3 id="installation">Installation</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Clone the repo
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git clone https://github.com/acrucetta/chicago_COVID_app.git
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Install Environment
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">source</span> .venv/bin/activate
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run the application in your local server
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>python myapp.py
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>
